import React from 'react'
import {  Item } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const ItemExampleItems = (props) => (
  <Item.Group>
    <Item>
      

      <Item.Content>
        <Item.Header as='a'>Header</Item.Header>
    <Item.Meta>Difficulty: {props.list.difficulty}</Item.Meta>
        <Item.Meta>Would Take Again: {props.list.takeAgain} </Item.Meta>
        <Item.Meta>Is TextBook Requierd: {props.list.isTextBook} </Item.Meta>
        <Item.Description>
        {props.list.body}
        </Item.Description>

      </Item.Content>
    </Item>


  </Item.Group>
)

export default ItemExampleItems
